spans.text: mad Each fond idea of the blessings past ; Blessings which only to the anguish add ; OH , did their pleasing efficacy
of his tender opening unfledged years
The wonder of our drooping isle
hold his many virtues in your view , Then must a freewill offering escape your hands
must a freewill offering escape your hands
a freewill offering escape your hands
blooming on , spite of the frosty blast
full ripe — how rich the sweet repast
ripe — how rich the sweet repast
That separates the friend we lightly prise
how can I but feel the dire effect , Where infancy began the social tie , Which still increased , void of the least defect , As each revolving year did multiply
the social tie , Which still increased , void of the least defect , As each revolving year did multiply
void of the least defect , As each revolving year
mouldering to his own primaeval dust
Lifting the ravished sense to heights supreme , Again with fancy painted woes elate
the passions of the tragic theme
each reigning vice In strongest colours of their genuine hue
within the bowels of the earth
